<i>He is long gone.</i>

1:06:14.762 --> 1:06:17.139
<i>What were you and Ms. Gu
talking about back there?</i>

1:06:20.893 --> 1:06:22.979
<i>Don't you ever approach my family again.</i>

1:06:23.062 --> 1:06:24.605
But why did you?

1:06:27.233 --> 1:06:28.901
<i>I can't trust myself.</i>

1:06:28.985 --> 1:06:32.446
<i>I feel like I did something awful to her.</i>

1:06:32.530 --> 1:06:34.532
<i>You never had any respect for me.</i>

1:06:35.408 --> 1:06:36.575
Are you trying to get revenge?

1:06:36.659 --> 1:06:38.244
<i>I'm giving you a warning.</i>

1:06:38.327 --> 1:06:40.454
<i>I won't sit still this time.</i>

